Here is the correct production-grade build order for Bushmarket (strict sequence):
🧱 1. SYSTEM FOUNDATION (DO THIS FIRST)
👉 This is where everything depends on.
You build:
Project structure (FastAPI backend)
Environment config (.env)
PostgreSQL connection
Base ORM setup (SQLAlchemy Base)
Migration system (Alembic)
Redis connection (for events + cache)
Kafka connection (event bus skeleton)
